Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.27,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Dung-dugudung-dung ....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.32,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Obrolan sekolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.38,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kalau disingkat jadi Olan-kolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.32,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Ya, silakan!
