Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.00,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ah ... omong-omong,\Nkalian satu sekolah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.80,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Yap! SMA Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.96,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kami masuk ke sana\Nkarena dekat dari rumah.
