Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.21,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Emang rumahmu enggak\Ndi sekitaran sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.22,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ah, enggak.
