Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.90,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,I-Ibuku menabung\Nuntuk pernikahanku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.40,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Tolong pakai ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.10,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai bekerja ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.67,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Jangan memperlakukan\Nkami kayak perampok, heh!
